WEBVTT

00:00.361 --> 00:03.803
<i>(Michael) My name is Michael Westen.</I>
<i>i used to be a spy until...</i></i>

00:03.824 --> 00:04.406
[ Cellphone rings ]

00:04.462 --> 00:07.011
(Man) We got a burn notice
on you. You're blacklisted.

00:07.079 --> 00:09.468
<i>When you're burned,</i>
<i>you've got nothing --</i>

00:09.536 --> 00:12.148
<i>no cash, no credit,</i>
<i>no job history.</i>

00:12.216 --> 00:14.529
<i>You're stuck in whatever city</i>
<i>they decide to dump you in.</i>

00:14.597 --> 00:16.604
Where am I?
Miami.

00:16.672 --> 00:19.825
<i>You do whatever work</i>
<i>comes your way.</i>

00:19.892 --> 00:22.477
<i>You rely on anyone</i>
<i>who's still talking to you.</i>

00:22.545 --> 00:24.084
<i>A trigger-happy</i>
<i>ex-girlfriend...</i>

00:24.152 --> 00:25.730
Should we shoot them?

00:25.797 --> 00:28.347
<i>...An old friend who used</i>
<i>to inform on you to the FBI...</i>

00:28.415 --> 00:30.726
You know spies --
a bunch of bitchy little girls.

00:30.794 --> 00:33.271
<i>...Family, too...</i>
<i>Hey, is that your mom again?</i>

00:33.339 --> 00:35.454
<i>...If you're desperate.</i>
<i>Someone needs your help, Michael.</i>

00:35.522 --> 00:37.966
<i>Bottom line --</i>
<i>as long as you're burned,</i>

00:38.033 --> 00:39.642
<i>you're not going anywhere.</i>

